{"tid":1831712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢肺炎呢家嘢，最怕係死亡率唔太高，而係傳播速度太快","createTime":"2020-01-20T14:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T04:22:42.000Z","uid":35699,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"b2784b80aa44889f8fc0147035417f7e54697530","tid":1831712,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:54:36.000Z","msg":"依家大陸掩咗一個月，終於開始爆煲，如果呢隻病毒死亡率高，快快趣趣死晒班感染者，反而無事可以甩難<br />\n<br />\n但如果唔係惹到三幾日就釘蓋，呢隻病將會消耗支那大量醫療器材、藥物，同埋本來都好缺嘅醫療人手，再配合支那高超嘅衛生水平同埋近乎瘋狂嘅農曆年人口流動，只要一出現多幾個大城市大爆發，呢件事起碼搞到五六月，到時使咗幾百億撲殺病情，又消耗所餘無幾嘅外匯同埋勞動力，今次真係支爆了"},{"pid":"33745e987b630fb78b9baea4310b2cb7dbf5fa52","tid":1831712,"uid":28818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9d776ec6b99b70e1bbc869ed530e1473e354a4","tid":1831712,"uid":269481,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"玩得多Plague Inc就知點解架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17ff58838dc589578a587c83f3364f27416c1499","tid":1831712,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"2a9d776ec6b99b70e1bbc869ed530e1473e354a4","tid":1831712,"uid":269481,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:04:24.000Z","msg":"玩得多Plague Inc就知點解架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34f14c4efd6582d765e61e8f92037af33c426b1f","tid":1831712,"uid":118888,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-20T15:08:05.000Z","msg":"病毒會變異<br />\n呢點大家都會忽略<br />\n但專家會好怕<br />\n<br 